add_move_rule_type
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
add_move_rule_type

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_move_rule_type -  This method puts up a request to move a rule from one type to another.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int add_move_rule_type(string area,
int rule_no,
int type,
string creator)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^area%^RESET%^ - the area to do the move in
%^BOLD%^rule_no%^RESET%^ - the rule number to move
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type to move the rule to
%^BOLD%^creator%^RESET%^ - the creator of this request
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/inherit/player_council.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method puts up a request to move a rule from one type to another.
.EP

